Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.80,0:02:07.00,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝能力者所拥有的心之故事背后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:10.62,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,一定都隐藏有丑陋的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:13.08,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:19.58,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,美丽的故事背后也许是不可告人的痛苦回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.31,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这是逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:02:59.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是梦...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.42,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,藏在我心灵深处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:19.92,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不能被任何人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.12,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:39.84,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:42.55,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,已经
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:44.09,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,过去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.51,0:03:59.26,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:03.46,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不愧是至今为止遇到的最厉害的爱丽丝能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:06.36,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,虽然要对付你们可没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:09.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是这场胜利是属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.29,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就算人多也不会输给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.87,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,恶魔之羽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:45.35,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.35,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:56.42,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,脱离我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:04:58.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就是我要说的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:02.33,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,现在开始会遇到越来越强的对手的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大家一起战斗不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:05.98,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:06.99,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.60,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:10.31,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊～好巧哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:47.63,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:50.07,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,这个应该是我要说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:54.89,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,其实应该是我脱离你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.18,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:01.64,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么  你想要这个苹果做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.28,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.58,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大概是苹果派之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:09.23,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我想做果酱  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.45,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:14.01,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,为了苹果而战斗的爱丽丝能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:17.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是大家烹调的方法是不同的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:23.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,用对手的丑陋的心来阻止对手进攻是我的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.65,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你很不爽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.16,0:06:26.82,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:31.40,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,夺取心之故事就可以让对手幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.97,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,把对方内心的黑暗解放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:38.23,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,相反应该被感谢才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:40.89,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不用再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:42.79,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:46.46,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:50.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:53.62,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,需要被解放吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:18.75,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真的  你不需要被解放吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:26.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,罗莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:34.33,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,雾香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:37.74,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,会喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:42.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没有哪个女生会不喜欢芝士蛋糕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:44.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:48.23,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,雾香学姐可不是普通的女性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:49.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:58.11,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我也不认为明日香的方法是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.55,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是如果有别的什么方法的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.47,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我是不会认同她的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.06,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.76,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不可思议的这一天却如平时一样是个好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:32.81,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,罗莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.65,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是你的祝福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.26,0:08:44.41,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好可怜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.69,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那么小就...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.47,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,父母因为事故而死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:52.34,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我却没有觉得悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:57.29,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,终于可以从父母的教育中解放出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.08,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,世界变得明亮起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:05.72,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:08.12,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我获得自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.26,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,成绩优秀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:15.27,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就能靠奖学金生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:19.94,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我毫无疑问地跳级进入大学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:30.72,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,同学和老师都因此疏远了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.22,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就是开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:40.55,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,对连什么是趣事都不知道的我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:42.56,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,想拥有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.16,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,大概是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.03,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那个  你也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.87,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那次相遇只是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:10.67,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,她的名字是罗莉娜·丽丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:16.37,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,她拿着开启奇迹空间的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:20.62,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拥有共同的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:24.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,让我和她之间的关系变得亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.42,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,来这边啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:41.46,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:07.27,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我想了解这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:11.39,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,因为奇迹空间才与罗莉娜相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.54,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,才成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.27,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那是个重要的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:19.90,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我觉得了解这里就如同了解她一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:22.02,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,所以就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:26.78,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,研究奇迹空间也是因为她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.11,0:11:40.22,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,她的存在日益变得重要起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.99,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是从那天开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:44.29,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,92
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:46.31,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,93
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.16,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,94
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.10,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,95
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:52.65,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,96
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.20,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,97
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:57.52,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,98
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:11:59.90,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,99
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:02.31,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,100
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.21,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那不过是一直玩的躲猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:50.08,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,只不过是个恶作剧而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:54.81,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,只是想观察她慌张的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.26,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,本来打算马上就打开的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.53,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,罗莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.18,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,罗莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:31.75,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:32.90,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,请喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:34.29,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:37.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,在写「永不终结的爱丽斯」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:38.68,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.13,0:14:40.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还差好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:47.00,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好想读一读哥哥写的「永不终结的爱丽斯」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:50.97,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不用那么吃惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:51.85,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:53.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.97,0:14:55.02,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,害羞？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:14:56.34,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:59.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好像自己的心被看透了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:03.88,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,啊～那有只在打洞的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.33,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.76,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:18.58,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,奇迹空间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.60,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:39.73,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:49.43,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,住...住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:56.06,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你的心之故事所藏着的丑陋  我会把它呼唤出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.36,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,恶魔之羽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.47,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.31,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,罗莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:28.71,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,每年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.83,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,都来这看望我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.27,0:16:33.01,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.39,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,罗莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:36.22,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,忌日吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:39.25,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哦  好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:43.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.35,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,并没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.66,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我在那之后被人救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.38,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你不会不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:02.67,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,如你所想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:08.72,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我和你的那一天开始就疏远了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:10.24,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,够了  住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.69,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:17.54,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你对我做了那么过分的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:18.93,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.50,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我本来想马上就救你出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:27.91,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,在那么狭窄那么黑暗的地方  我叫了多少次你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:32.46,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你真是太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:36.57,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,为了逃避我的离开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:38.02,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你把我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:39.95,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,视为死去的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:45.27,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是的  罗莉娜并没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:51.47,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,因此我才...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:58.05,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,只是为了逃避失去朋友对我的打击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:01.47,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,把她视为死去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:04.75,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,罗莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:13.33,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,心之扉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:14.91,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,秘之扉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:18.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,成为开启那扇门的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.87,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,把心之故事展现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:42.54,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,原来是因为小时候的事才停留在那时的状态吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.47,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,雾香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:53.86,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,她已经
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:56.21,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不是爱丽丝能力者了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.40,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.17,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:12.47,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不要碰它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:17.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.73,0:19:24.35,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:30.54,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:32.32,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,把你的心之故事也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:44.99,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,最初与你们套近乎就是为了把你们的心之故事都夺取了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:48.24,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我的白之羽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.90,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,纯白之羽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.69,0:19:53.10,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,以纯洁美丽的羽之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.61,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,展现出记忆中的黑暗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.13,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:12.82,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.22,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我的能力没有用？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.02,0:20:18.80,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,为什么没有把记忆之门打开呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.71,0:20:20.59,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,有栖川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:21.99,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,纪纱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.48,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,下次再分胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:28.45,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,纪纱没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.21,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:31.64,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,有栖川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:33.67,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,有栖川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:37.53,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.69,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:42.50,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:51.29,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,已经没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.85,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,嗯  没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.35,0:20:56.03,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,给你添了不少麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:59.57,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,已经不能再一起战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:01.77,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,反正已经过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:06.76,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,之后我想只能在一边协助你们而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:10.58,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,不过  这次发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:14.09,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,就算是因为逃避导致的永别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:17.05,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,确实是在利用对心之故事的逃避吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:20.31,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,也算是对欺骗自己心灵的惩罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:22.60,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,并不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:24.92,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,并不是逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.54,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,那是拯救的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:32.71,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,拯救的...故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:37.13,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,因为心之故事雾香学姐才被拯救的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:39.66,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,为了不使自己受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.31,0:21:58.21,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,为什么没有把记忆之门打开呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:08.92,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.87,0:22:12.68,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,什么也想不起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:02.49,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,没想过和绮罗叶战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:06.44,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,如果你们互相争斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:08.68,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,我就可以省不少力了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.48,0:24:11.86,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,但是不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.64,0:24:15.91,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你有不得不打倒绮罗叶的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:19.95,zhengwen,,0,0,0,,你也察觉到了不是吗？
